    "description": "操控矮人机甲，与你的学者飞龙并肩飞行。在这款富有剧情的动作生存 RPG 中，建造基地、探索世界、抵御敌袭，揭开天空中破碎世界的秘密。<br><br><strong>First Dwarf</strong> 融合了 RPG 成长系统、殖民地生存玩法和战略建造机制，背景设定在一个魔法被污染、岛屿漂浮在空中的幻想世界。你可以单人游戏，也可以联机合作，共同对抗德里夫特兰的危险。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/4912ec1380380c2517506d1b24329b6d.poster.avif?t=1772243007\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/4912ec1380380c2517506d1b24329b6d.webm?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/4912ec1380380c2517506d1b24329b6d.mp4?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在危险的浮空岛上建造殖民地，使用炮塔、围墙和资源系统。合理布局，抵御怪物攻击和自然灾害，如火山爆发与污染风暴。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e4e3407e3024274618fe856be21677bb.poster.avif?t=1772243007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e4e3407e3024274618fe856be21677bb.webm?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e4e3407e3024274618fe856be21677bb.mp4?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>制作机甲升级、武器、装备、防御工具和各种装置。收集稀有资源并解锁蓝图，打造属于你的个性化战斗风格。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e60ca38c05ecf56299fee9fb9d56c4eb.poster.avif?t=1772243007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e60ca38c05ecf56299fee9fb9d56c4eb.webm?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/e60ca38c05ecf56299fee9fb9d56c4eb.mp4?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在被魔法撕裂的世界中求生。与突变怪物战斗，管理资源，做出关键抉择——你会拯救被污染的生物，还是将它们净化以保护你的定居地？<br><br>德里夫特兰曾是一个完整的世界，如今因法师战争四分五裂。矮人是最后的文明。你是特鲁，一位新的“第一矮人”，驾驶强大机甲、在飞龙拉格纳的帮助下踏上任务，寻找希望与真相。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/986ad2917b5febaa5ada7a791449f093.poster.avif?t=1772243007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/986ad2917b5febaa5ada7a791449f093.webm?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/986ad2917b5febaa5ada7a791449f093.mp4?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索古老遗迹、生物群落和神秘岛屿，揭开埃斯科伊姆族的秘密，研究失落科技，召集其他矮人工会，一起重夺天空。<br><br>驾驶可自定义的飞艇在殖民地之间快速移动。升级盔甲、解锁技能，自由定制机甲外观。从地底洞穴到炙热悬崖，每座岛屿都有一段传说等你发现。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/133629f7118e1062da36c73095a8e467.poster.avif?t=1772243007\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/133629f7118e1062da36c73095a8e467.webm?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714900/extras/133629f7118e1062da36c73095a8e467.mp4?t=1772243007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用近战武器、远程装备、机甲技能与自动防御设施抵御被污染的生物。每场战斗都是一次战术和技术的挑战，每一次胜利都带来希望。<br><br><strong>建造</strong>你的殖民地、<strong>打造</strong>你的装备、<strong>探索</strong>奇幻天空、<strong>战斗</strong>未来、<strong>生存</strong>下去。<br>成为“第一矮人”，书写属于你的传奇！",
